# Loyalty — Internal Points Expiry Trigger
# M10-S08: GCP Cloud Scheduler calls this endpoint at 02:00 UTC daily.
# In production this is called by GCP Cloud Scheduler (network-protected).
# M115-S03 adds X-Internal-Key guard.
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @beloauto/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @beloauto/backend run dev

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### POST /internal/loyalty/expire-points — run daily expiry
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/loyalty/expire-points

###
